            "type": "text",
            "text": "Optimize Ben2 for background removal by implementing batch processing to reduce latency. Use caching mechanisms for frequently processed images, and set appropriate timeouts for API calls. Monitor rate limits to prevent throttling, and leverage CDN for image delivery. For high-throughput scenarios, consider load balancing across multiple API instances and compress images before transmission to minimize bandwidth."
