            "text": "Common issues include invalid image formats, exceeded rate limits, or processing timeouts. Implement retry logic with exponential backoff for transient errors. Log detailed error codes from API responses, such as 400 for bad requests or 503 for service unavailable. Use health checks to monitor API availability, and maintain fallback mechanisms for critical workflows. Regularly update your client libraries to incorporate the latest Ben2 improvements and bug fixes."
